<div class="panel panel-info">
	<div class="panel-body">
		<p>This interface allows you to search for tweets in the past. Twitter allows search and retrieval of tweets up to 1 week ago.</p>
		<p>If you have any stored Twitter Searches they will be listed here.</p>
		<p><b>NB:</b> You are allowed to run only 1 Twitter Stream or Search queries at a time. If you do not see the 'New' button, wait for one of your other queries to finish.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<% if current_user.twitter_searches.size > 0 %>
<div id="twitter-search-list">
	<%= render 'twitter_searches/list' %>
</div>
<br>
<% end %>
<% if current_user.has_open_twitter_slots? %>
<%= link_to 'New Twitter Search', new_user_twitter_search_path, :class => 'btn btn-info' %><br><br>
<% else %>
<p>Please wait until your previous Twitter searches or streams have finished before adding a new one.</p>
<% end %>
<%= link_to 'Back', :root, :class => 'btn btn-default' %>